      </p>

      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <a href="mailto:tom@ctautomation.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-coral-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-coral-400 transition-all hover:scale-105 transform text-lg mb-6">
